</span><span class='line'>&lt;code&gt;
</span><span class='line'>之后在浏览器输入localhost:4000就可以查看了。
</span><span class='line'>5. 部署到Github
</span><span class='line'>在Github上新建一个Repository，命名为<span class="sb">`</span>username.github.io<span class="sb">`</span>。然后在cmd中进行部署。
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code&gt;bash
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">cd</span> <span class="se">\&amp;</span>lt<span class="p">;</span>wherever_your_octopress_is&gt;
</span><span class='line'>rake setup_github_pages
</span><span class='line'>&lt;a <span class="nv">href</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;https://github.com/your_username/your_username.github.io&quot;</span>&gt;https://github.com/your_username/your_username.github.io&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;rake deploy&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;rake new_post<span class="o">[</span>title of post<span class="o">]</span>
</span><span class='line'>rake new_site<span class="o">[</span>name of site<span class="o">]</span>&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;rake generate&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;rake deploy
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
访问username.github.io即可查看，可能会有延迟，一般不超过1分钟。</p>
